name: ONE of ONE of ONE | ISSUE 1/4
description:
this is your wallet identifier represented by a series of seemingly random monochromatic glyphs ranging from skull white to ink black, scattered amongst an eternal sea of shades of grey, representing the steps on the road to understanding

you are encouraged to stare carefully while pondering your role within this system of chaos we call life

this unique 1/1 goes a step further by adding an additional dimension, ensuring each viewer has their own unique, persistent version of this nft, essentially turning it into a 1/1/1 edition
